Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Generosity 慷慨
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}新的一天開始\NThe day begins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}她打理好自己的容貌\NShe makes herself look pure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我知道她會轉頭的\NI know she'll turn some heads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我敢跟你保證\Nof that I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你看看她，如此華麗\NNow you know she's looking fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}如此崇高，如此神聖\NAll so divine, all so sublime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}她還要工作\NShe gets to work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你不知道針要趕快補？\NDon't you know a stitch in time saves nine?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}當大家看到她走過來\NWhen they all see her come around,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}就知道有什麼特別的\Nyou know there's something here to be found
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心中湧出美麗\Nthe lush beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}如同鑽戒一般\Nlike a diamond ring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}它是如此的珍奇\Nof the highest Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}它的美麗不只這樣\NAnd even more beautiful inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}再深入點你就知道\Nreach way down deep and I'm sure you'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}她能給你\Nthat she can bring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那顆所謂的\Nthat little something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慷慨的心\Ncalled Generosity
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}如此優雅，她跳著華爾滋穿過人群\NSo elegant, as she waltzes across the room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}看她閃耀\NWatch her shine now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}視線都在她身上\NHer time, it will come soon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我們不要管這麼多了\NNow let's use just what we know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}來吧，我們一起跳隻舞\NC'mon now let's go, go, go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我們別管時間了\NAnd dance the night away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}就一起跳到最後一刻\Nuntil we all have to go home
