Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}來看月光照耀那雙水藍的眼睛\NNow come watch the moonlight reflect off her sapphire eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)}我要跟你在一起到永遠－\NI'll stick by you forever and every single day-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}－我們的關係只會越來越親密\N-to forge and reinforce the bonds that tie us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}大家一起完成這和聲\NNow come and join me in harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}這是我人生最美好的事情\NThis is the best possible thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}她會在這等著你們\NShe'll be here waiting
