Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我好奇著一些事情\Nas I lay my head down to slumber
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)}我把時間編在一起\NI weave through time
